  itemName: Heartseeker
  itemDescription: The founding blade of the Root Warden cult, used in every initiation
    rite for two hundred years. It was last seen buried in the chest of the cult's
    final high priest, who pulled it out himself, said something no witness could
    later agree upon, and walked out into the corrupted forest without stopping.
